data.description: Move by the holidays into this West Florence gem that offers 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths with over 2000 sq ft. Prime location on a corner lot in the sought after West Pointe subdivision.  Large front porch, 2-car garage, vinyl fenced in backyard with a covered screened patio, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or gatherings.  This house also has a detached finished building that has electricity and water.  There is a bathroom, water heater and A/C unit included also.  A potential in-law suite, business or income opportunity...the possibilities are endless!  The grand foyer is offset by the dining room adorned with crown molding. Straight across is the laundry/mudroom with garage entry.  The great room has a fireplace, soaring cathedral ceilings and leads to back patio.  Natural light shines throughout as does the laminate wood flooring and brand new carpet.  Cabinets galore offer ample storage solutions in the spacious eat-in kitchen that offers stainless steel appliances and ceramic tile.  The owner's retreat is highlighted by gorgeous tray ceilings and the ensuite features a jetted tub, double vanity, shower and walk-in closet.   You could be creating new memories in your new home for the holidays!
